	<script is:inline>document.body.classList.add('som-page');</script>

	<!-- =============== HERO =============== -->
	<section class:list={["som-hero", heroBgUrl && "has-bg"]} style={heroBgUrl ? `--som-hero-bg: url('${heroBgUrl}')` : undefined}>
		<div class="som-hero-cross" aria-hidden="true">†</div>
		<div class="som-hero-grid">
			<div class="som-hero-text">
				<p class="som-hero-eyebrow">The Kohler Group, PLLC · Huntersville, NC</p>
				<h1>
					Your Marriage<br />
					Can Be <em>Saved.</em>
				</h1>
				<p class="som-hero-subtitle">But not with another hour of weekly counseling.</p>
				<div class="som-hero-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="som-hero-media">
				{videoUrl ? (
					<div class="som-hero-video">
						<iframe
							src={videoUrl}
							title="A Message from Barbara"
							loading="lazy"
							allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
							allowfullscreen
						></iframe>
					</div>
				) : (
					<div class="som-hero-video som-hero-video--placeholder" aria-label="Video coming soon">
						<div class="som-video-play-icon" aria-hidden="true"></div>
						<p>Video Coming Soon</p>
					</div>
				)}
				<div class="som-hero-cta">
					<a href="#screener" class="som-btn-primary">Take the Next Step</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<p class="som-hero-body som-hero-body-full">
			The 5-Day Marriage Intensive is for couples who are done drifting, done fighting, and ready — truly ready — to do something transformative. For couples who believe their marriage is worth everything it takes.
		</p>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== TRUTH STRIP =============== -->
	<section class="som-truth-strip">
		<blockquote>"What God has joined together, let no man separate."</blockquote>
		<cite>Matthew 19:6 · NASB</cite>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== PILLARS =============== -->
	<section id="different" class="som-different-section">
		<div class="som-container">
			<div class="som-section-header">
				<p class="som-section-label">Why This Works</p>
				<h2 class="som-section-title">This Is Not Typical Marriage Therapy.<br /><em>This Is Transformation.</em></h2>
				<p class="som-section-body">
					Most couples have been to counselors. Many have been to multiple counselors. What they haven't experienced is a clinical process that addresses the root — spiritually, neurologically, and emotionally — in concentrated, consecutive days of focused work.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="som-pillars-grid">
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">01</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>Five Consecutive Days of Focused Work</h3>
					<p>Weekly 50-minute sessions have a ceiling. Real change requires sustained time. Five uninterrupted days create the momentum and depth that months of weekly sessions rarely reach.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">02</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>Four Clinical Modalities Working Together</h3>
					<p>Re-Decision Therapy, EMDR, HeartSync, Judicial Prayer and TRET address your marriage on every level — the early decisions you made about yourself, the lies and/or trauma stored in the deepest parts of your psyche as well as your body, and the spiritual fragmentation that talk therapy cannot touch.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">03</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>Faith-Integrated &amp; Clinically Grounded</h3>
					<p>Barbara holds a Master's degree in Rehabilitation Counseling Studies which looks at the client holistically. She has been licensed as an LCMHC (Licensed Clinical Mental Health Counselor) since 2002, and is an ordained minister. She brings 30 years of clinical excellence and the power of Christ-centered prayer into the same room — because healing requires a multidimensional approach.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">04</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>You Work on the Root, Not Just the Symptoms</h3>
					<p>Most couples fight about money, kids, and sex. But those aren't the real issues. The real issues are the early decisions each of you made about your worth, your safety, and what love looks like — formed long before you ever met.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">05</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>100% Client Satisfaction Reported</h3>
					<p>Our clients surveyed report being completely satisfied with their Marriage Intensive experience and 100% said they would recommend it to others.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-pillar">
					<div class="som-pillar-number">06</div>
					<div class="som-pillar-accent"></div>
					<h3>Couples Travel From Across the Country</h3>
					<p>Couples travel from across the Carolinas and the entire United States to work with Barbara. This is not local-only care — it is a nationally recognized specialized program you cannot find everywhere.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== COUPLE THUMBNAILS STRIP =============== -->
	<section class="som-couples-strip" aria-label="Couples Barbara has worked with">
		<div class="som-couples-grid">
			{coupleThumbs.map((c) => (
				<img
					src={c.url}
					alt={c.alt}
					width="600"
					height="600"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
				/>
			))}
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== WHO THIS IS FOR =============== -->
	<section class="som-who-section">
		<div class="som-container">
			<div class="som-two-col">
				<div>
					<p class="som-section-label">Who This Is For</p>
					<h2 class="som-section-title" style="font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,44px)">You May Be Ready<br />If <em>This Is You</em></h2>
					<p class="som-section-body" style="margin:0;max-width:100%;margin-bottom:32px;font-size:14px;">
						Couples arrive at the Marriage Intensive from different places. What they share is a willingness to stop surviving and start truly living together.
					</p>
					<ul class="som-who-list">
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You've been to counseling before — maybe multiple counselors — and you're still in the same place.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You've experienced betrayal, affair, or a devastating rupture you don't know how to heal.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You're on a slow drift and you recognize it — and you're ready to stop.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Your faith matters to you, and you want a counselor who takes that seriously — not just tolerates it.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You're willing to come to Huntersville, NC for five days and invest fully in the process.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You sense there's a depth of connection and freedom you haven't reached — and you want it.</span></li>
						<li><span class="som-who-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>You want to have a biblical marriage where you both experience walking as heirs together of the grace of life (1 Peter 3:7).</span></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<div class="som-stat-box">
						<div class="som-stat-number">18+</div>
						<div class="som-stat-label">Years of Clinical Experience Working with Couples</div>
						<p class="som-stat-caption">"I have walked alongside couples carrying some of the heaviest things imaginable — betrayal, generational trauma, years of disconnection. And I have watched God move in those marriages in ways that were, honestly, remarkable."</p>
						<div style="height:24px;"></div>
						<div class="som-stat-number">30+</div>
						<div class="som-stat-label">Years of Experience Working in the Counseling Field, Including Business Executives, Entrepreneurs, and the Families Who Enable Them to Be Successful</div>
					</div>
					<div style="margin-top:2px;background:var(--som-sapphire);padding:32px 40px;">
						<div class="som-stat-number" style="color:var(--som-gold-light);">100%</div>
						<div class="som-stat-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Client Satisfaction Rate</div>
						<p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);font-weight:300;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">Post-intensive surveys show every respondent said the program met their goals and that they would recommend it to others.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== BARBARA BIO =============== -->
	<section class="som-bio-section">
		<div class="som-bio-inner">
			<div>
				<img
					src={barbaraPhotoUrl}
					alt="Barbara Kohler, MS, CRC, LCMHC, NCC"
					width="800"
					height="1067"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
					class="som-bio-portrait"
				/>
			</div>
			<div class="som-bio-text">
				<p class="som-section-label" style="text-align:left">Your Guide</p>
				<h2 class="som-section-title" style="font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,40px);text-align:left;margin-bottom:16px;">Barbara Kohler</h2>
				<div class="som-bio-credentials">
					<span class="som-cred-tag">MS</span>
					<span class="som-cred-tag">CRC</span>
					<span class="som-cred-tag">LCMHC</span>
					<span class="som-cred-tag">NCC</span>
					<span class="som-cred-tag">Licensed Since 2002</span>
					<span class="som-cred-tag">Ordained Minister</span>
				</div>
				<p>Barbara Kohler is the Founder and CEO of The Kohler Group, PLLC — a faith-integrated Christian psychotherapy practice located in Huntersville, NC, serving the greater Charlotte and Lake Norman area, with in person and telehealth across North and South Carolina.</p>
				<p>She has been a Licensed Clinical Mental Health Counselor since 2002 and holds National Certified Counselor credentials since 2009. She is also an ordained minister — a distinction that shapes every aspect of how she works with couples.</p>
				<p>Barbara uses a multidimensional approach in working with individuals and couples. She integrates several powerful, effective modalities including EMDR, Re-Decision Therapy, HeartSync, Judicial Prayer, and TRET. Her approach addresses marriages at the root of each individual's life, to enable the couple to set aside toxic blaming and deal with spiritual fractures that have never been fully healed. <a href="https://thekohlergroup.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--som-gold);text-decoration:underline;">Visit thekohlergroup.net</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== INVESTMENT =============== -->
	<section class="som-investment-section">
		<p class="som-section-label" style="color:var(--som-gold-light)">Your Investment</p>
		<h2 class="som-section-title">What It Costs to<br /><em>Save Your Marriage</em></h2>
		<p class="som-section-body">
			Consider what divorce costs — financially, spiritually, and in the lives of your children. The Marriage Intensive is not inexpensive. But for couples who are serious, it is one of the most significant investments they will ever make.
		</p>
		<div class="som-investment-price">{price}</div>
		<div style="margin-top:24px;"></div>
		<p class="som-investment-duration" style="color:var(--som-gold-light);">Five Consecutive Days</p>
		<p class="som-investment-duration" style="margin-top:-16px;color:var(--som-gold-light);">Includes All Assessments, Educational Materials, and Personality Survey</p>
		<p class="som-investment-duration" style="margin-top:-16px;color:var(--som-gold-light);">Post Intensive Coaching Package Available for Purchase</p>
		<div style="height:16px;"></div>
		<p class="som-investment-duration" style="margin-top:-16px;color:var(--som-gold-light);">(Travel and Lodging Is at Your Own Expense)</p>
		<div class="som-investment-includes">
			<span class="som-include-item">Five full clinical days</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">Pre-intensive consultation</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">Re-Decision Therapy</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">EMDR</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">HeartSync</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">Judicial Prayer</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">TRET</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">Faith-integrated prayer</span>
			<span class="som-include-item">Post-intensive planning</span>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== QUIZ / SCREENER =============== -->
	<section id="screener" class="som-widget-section">
		<div class="som-container">
			<div class="som-section-header">
				<p class="som-section-label">First Step</p>
				<h2 class="som-section-title">Is the Marriage Intensive<br /><em>Right for You?</em></h2>
				<p class="som-section-body">
					Answer eight short questions. If it looks like a good fit, you'll be invited to schedule a complimentary 30-minute consultation with Barbara — no obligation, no pressure.
				</p>
			</div>
			<MarriageIntensiveQuiz
				barbaraEmail={barbaraEmail}
				bookingUrl={bookingUrl}
				phone={phone}
			/>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- =============== TESTIMONIALS =============== -->
	{testimonials && testimonials.length > 0 && (
		<section id="testimonials" class="som-testimonials-section">
			<div class="som-container">
				<div class="som-section-header">
					<p class="som-section-label">Client Testimonials</p>
					<h2 class="som-section-title">Stories of <em>Transformation</em></h2>
					<p class="som-section-body">
						Words from couples who chose to do the hard, beautiful work. To protect their privacy, all identifying details have been removed.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="som-testimonials-grid">
					{testimonials.map((t: any) => (
						<article class="som-testimonial">
							<p class="som-testimonial-mark" aria-hidden="true">"</p>
							<p class="som-testimonial-quote">{t.quote}</p>
						</article>
					))}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	)}

	<!-- =============== FOOTER =============== -->
	<footer class="som-footer">
		<p class="som-footer-name">The Kohler Group, PLLC</p>
		<p class="som-footer-meta">Barbara Kohler, MS, CRC, LCMHC, NCC · Licensed Since 2002</p>
		<p class="som-footer-meta">13420 Reese Blvd West, Daetwyler Plaza, Huntersville, NC 28078</p>
		<div class="som-footer-links">
			<a href="https://thekohlergroup.net">TheKohlerGroup.net</a>
			<a href="https://thekohlergroup.net/intensives/marriage">Marriage Intensives</a>
			<a href={`tel:${phone.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')}`}>Call Us</a>
			<a href="mailto:Ashley.Bostic@thekohlergroup.net">Email Us</a>
		</div>
		<p class="som-footer-legal">
			Barbara Kohler, MS, CRC, LCMHC, NCC is a Licensed Clinical Mental Health Counselor licensed in the State of North Carolina, and a Licensed Professional Counselor licensed in the State of South Carolina. Services are provided in accordance with the applicable licensure standards and ethics of the respective states and the ACA Code of Ethics. This website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a therapeutic relationship. Individual results vary. The Marriage Intensive program is a private-pay service; insurance is not accepted for intensive programs.
		</p>
	</footer>
